These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, nurse, accountant, dressmaker, chef
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, fuchsia, grey, lavender, lilac
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, golf, basketball, skateboarding, lacrosse
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the accountant is the accountant##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who likes yellow##1
 6. the chef is on the left of the accountant##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
10. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the chef is between the chinese and the person who likes lilac##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Job      | dancer        | nurse | chef     | accountant   | dressmaker |
| Color   | grey     | fuchsia      | lavender | lilac   | yellow    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Sport           | golf | basketball      | lacrosse     | skateboarding   | swimming     |

