.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
House: cottage, colonial, wooden, modern, victorian
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, family, superhero, spy, adventure
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, zinnia, sunflower, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the cottage house##1
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person watching documentary movies and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person who growssunflower is the colonial house##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is the wooden house##1
12. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| House         | modern | cottage | victorian    | colonial  | wooden    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | family     | documentary    | spy  | superhero     |
| Flower     | zinnia    | dahlia | balloon-flower | sunflower | azalea |

