.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, taxi, roller, helicopter, train
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, spanish, nigerian, polish
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia, lavender, white, orange
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person driving the train is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
 4. the indonesian is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 7. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the indonesian is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the nigerian##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the polish and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Transport         | ship | train     | roller   | taxi   | helicopter |
| Nationality   | polish  | canadian | indonesian | nigerian | spanish        |
| Color   | lavender      | fuchsia      | white       | orange       | pink       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

