There are 5 different favourite colors: turquise, black, ebony, blood-red, ivory
City: nizza, colone, hamburg, marseilles, rome
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is between the person who likes blood-red and the cottage house##2
 5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes black##1
 9. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
13. the person who likes black is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| House          | victorian  | townhouse     | cottage   | cape-cod     | farmhouse |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking    | singing  | skydiving | puzzles   |
