 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
