 3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the french##1
 5. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is between the freelancer and the fan of metal##2
 7. the fan of techno is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the coach is on the right of the french##1
10. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
11. the analyst is between the freelancer and the fan of metal##2
12. the person who likes red is on the right of the polish##1
13. the freelancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
