The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, swimming, lacrosse, golf
There are 5 different nationalities: french, indian, italian, polish, thai
 1. the polish is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is the italian##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the person eating lime is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person eating avocado is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the french##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person eating avocado and the person playing mah-jongg##2
12. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating lime##1
13. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
