5 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, monopoly, poker, scrabble
The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, writer, musician, electrician, architect
 1. the person playing scrabble is between the writer and the person playing snooker##2
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the writer is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the writer##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the architect##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
11. the musician is between the person playing monopoly and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Pet    | goat       | fish    | mouse | rat  | pony        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Game       | monopoly        | poker   | snooker  | scrabble   | backgammon |
| Job   | electrician       | musician      | architect      | entrepreneur | writer  |

