.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, august, may, june, september
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, red, aquamarine, ivory, orange
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, surfing, badminton, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's sport is climbing##2
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes red##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Birthday           | august | may | june | september    | july  |
| Color   | ivory  | red    | brown | aquamarine    | orange |
| Sport   | surfing  | climbing        | rowing   | badminton    | rugby     |

