.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, zucchini, grapes, cauliflower, broccoli
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, weightlifting, rowing, ice-hockey
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, cain, bongani, bolivar, havana
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the cain-smoker is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the fonseca-smoker##2
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating grapes is between the person driving the airplane and the person eating broccoli##2
 8. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating blueberry##2
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Food         | broccoli  | grapes | cauliflower   | zucchini      | blueberry |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | rowing    | cricket | ice-hockey | weightlifting      |
| Cigar           | bongani | cain    | fonseca       | bolivar     | havana      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

