.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: canasta, bridge, go, chess, mah-jongg
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, lily, rose, zinnia
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, aquamarine, fuchsia, lilac, mauve
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who likes lilac and the person who growszinnia##2
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who growstulip is between the person who likes mauve and the person who growslily##2
 6. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person playing chess is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the person who likes coral is the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | go    | mah-jongg  | bridge  | canasta      | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Flower   | lily | tulip    | zinnia    | rose       | amaryllis         |
| Color   | lilac  | aquamarine | mauve    | fuchsia     | coral      |

 